OL,3,CBoxer and part-time electrician Josh
OL,4,CPadley prepares for world title fight
OL,6,FOn Tuesday Josh Padley was working his
OL,7,Fday job, on the tools installing a
OL,8,Fsolar panel as an electrician in the
OL,9,Fnorth of England.
OL,11,FBut on Saturday, the 29-year-old will
OL,12,Ffight for the WBC lightweight title in
OL,13,FRiyadh, Saudi Arabia.
OL,15,FWorld champion Shakur Stevenson had
OL,16,Fbeen scheduled to face off against
OL,17,FAmerican Floyd Schofield.
