OL,6,FBut, after Schofield fell ill, it will
OL,7,Fbe Yorkshire-born boxer/electrician
OL,8,FPadley who will take on the life-
OL,9,Fchanging fight.
OL,11,FSpeaking to ITV News, Padley said: "It
OL,12,Fwas just a standard week really.
OL,13,FStandard Monday, Tuesday, I'd been to
OL,14,Fwork. I am a professional boxer, but I
OL,15,Falso have a day job.
OL,17,F"I'd just put my tea in the oven that
OL,18,Fnight and then we got the phone call
OL,19,Fthat every boxer dreams of.
