OL,4,CPadley prepares for world title fight
OL,6,FPadley will also come into the fight
OL,7,Fas an undefeated contender, coming off
OL,8,Fthe biggest win of his career after he
OL,9,Fbeat Mark Chamberlain at Wembley
OL,10,FStadium on the undercard of Anthony
OL,11,FJoshua vs Daniel Dubois in September
OL,12,F2024.
OL,14,FHis win in September was considered an
OL,15,Fupset. But if he could topple world
OL,16,Fchampion Stevenson at the weekend, it
OL,17,Fcould mark one of the biggest upsets
OL,18,Fin boxing.
