OL,6,F"When we landed yesterday, obviously
OL,7,Fwe got sorted out and then we went to
OL,8,Fthe gym for an hour for a little
OL,9,Fshakeout and hit a few pads.
OL,11,F"We watched a few clips on him and
OL,12,Fthat was my training for Shakur
